19 CONVICTED FELONS AND DELINQUENTS
20 A. Except as provided in subsection B of this section, it shall
21 be unlawful for any person convicted of any felony in any court of
22 this state or of another state or of the United States to have in
23 his or her possession or under his or her immediate control, or in
24 any vehicle which the person is operating, or at the residence where
