15 C. It shall be unlawful for any person serving a term of
16 probation for any felony in any court of this state or of another
17 state or of the United States or under the jurisdiction of any
18 alternative court program to have in his or her possession or under
19 his or her immediate control, or at his or her residence, or in any
20 passenger vehicle which the person is operating, any pistol, shotgun
21 or rifle including any imitation or homemade pistol, altered air or
22 toy pistol, toy shotgun or toy rifle, while such person is subject
23 to supervision, probation, parole or inmate status.
