4 F. Any person having been issued a handgun license pursuant to
5 the provisions of the Oklahoma Self-Defense Act and who knowingly or
6 intentionally allows a convicted felon or adjudicated delinquent or
7 a youthful offender as prohibited by the provisions of subsection A,
8 C, or D of this section to possess or have control of any firearm
